SUMMARY:Charter Review Commission Meeting
LOCATION:Tampa Old City Hall - Sister Cities Room 315 East Kennedy Bouleva
 rd Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:CHARTER REVIEW ADVISORY COMMISSION MEETING Date: Tuesday\, Jul
 y 14\, 2026 Time: 6:00pm to 9:00pm Location: Old City Hall  Sister Cities 
 Room 315 East Kennedy Boulevard Tampa\, Florida 33602 Facilitator Robert H
 endrickson will facilitate meetings of the 2025 Charter Review Advisory Co
 mmission. The commissions purpose is to review the Tampa Home Rule Charter
  of 1975\, as amended\, and propose any amendments or revisions by majorit
 y vote of the Commission\, and present a report with their recommendations
  to City Council\, which may by two-thirds vote of City Council be placed 
 on the ballot for a vote on March 2\, 2027. Meetings are scheduled monthly
  for the 2 nd and 4 th Tuesday. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/
 180081
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/180081
END:VEVENT
