 rter of 1975\, as amended\, and propose any amendments or revisions by maj
 ority vote of the Commission\, and present a report with their recommendat
 ions to City Council\, which may by two-thirds vote of City Council be pla
 ced on the ballot for a vote on March 2\, 2027. Meetings are scheduled mon
 thly for the 2 nd and 4 th Tuesday. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/n
 ode/180101
